{
  "title": "Data Models",
  "descriptions": [
    "The website’s content is separated into <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.json</span> files for fast editing and dynamic layout generation. All of the <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.json</span> files are stored in <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data</span> and use a unique data model."
  ],
  "content": [
    {
      "title": "Index Page",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The content is stored in <span class=\"roboto-mono\">index.json</span>. It's data model is an array of objects, and each object has the following data—"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "table": [
            [
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Key"
              },
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Description"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "title"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Section's name"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "section"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Type of cards the section will display."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Values",
                    "code": "\"About\", \"Case Studies\", \"Journal\", \"Press\", \"Events\", \"Press and Events\""
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "About Page",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The content is stored in <span class=\"roboto-mono\">about.json</span> and uses the following data models—"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "table": [
            [
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Key"
              },
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Description"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "card"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Content displayed on index page link"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "content"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "List of sections"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "array:object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Posts",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Articles and case studies are stored in separate <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.json</span> files under <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/journal</span> and <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/projects</span>. Articles and case studies share the same data model—"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "table": [
            [
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Key"
              },
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Description"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "title"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Article's name"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "description"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Summarizing caption"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "type"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Is the article a post or a case study?"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Values",
                    "code": "\"Post\", \"Case Study\""
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "date"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Date of publication"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "ruby Date object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "category"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Type of article"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "featured"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Will the journal post be featured on the index page?"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "bool"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "card"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Content displayed on index page link"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "links"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Header links, used primarily to reference to a project case study's website or source code"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "array:object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "meta"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Meta data and social media images"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "content"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "List of sections"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "array:object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "External Resources",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Press, events, case study tools, and post resources are stored in separate <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.json</span> files under <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/press</span>, <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/events</span>, <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/tools</span>, and <span class=\"roboto-mono\">/data/resources</span> . Each file uses the following data model—"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "table": [
            [
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Key"
              },
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Description"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "title"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Resource name"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "subtitle"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Resource's location name or author"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "action"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Call to action text that is displayed on hover"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "path"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Resource url path"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "profile"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Relative url path for <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.svg</span> profile image."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Meta",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Site's metadata and favicon content is stored in <span class=\"roboto-mono\">meta.json</span> and uses the following data model—"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "table": [
            [
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Key"
              },
              {
                "type": "header",
                "header": "Description"
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "url"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Website root url"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "site"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Twitter handle"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "type"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Metadata value-type"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Value",
                    "code": "\"website\""
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "card"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Social media card type"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Value",
                    "code": "summary"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "og"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Relative path to Open Graph social media card image"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "twitter"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Relative path to Twitter social media card image"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "string"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "favicons"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Stores Android and iOS favicon metadata"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "array:object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "tiles"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "<span class=\"roboto-monot\">ms-application</span> and <span class=\"\">theme-color</span> metadata."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "array:object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "type": "code",
                "code": "comments"
              },
              {
                "type": "descriptions",
                "descriptions": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Metadata HTML comments that referencing the Open Graph and Twitter metadata documentation and favicon generator GitHub repo."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "rule",
                    "title": "Type",
                    "code": "object"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
